name: Chris O‚ÄôCoin
tweet: I spent 8 years at Vice, cutting all kinds of amazing docs across all of the verticals and eventually landed in doc TV. All the while an avid watcher and admirer of Frontline, but, for whatever reason I thought the dream of one day cutting one seemed out of reach. (6/15)

name: Chris O‚ÄôCoin
tweet: So I went down my own path. Worked on feature documentaries, music videos, bts featurettes, industrials, short docs, long docs, commercials, concert films, live music, etc in all sorts of post roles. I eventually moved to NYC and wound up working for @Vice. (5/15)
